577
00:40:03,790 --> 00:40:05,990
If they can match up, they're free to go.

578
00:40:06,560 --> 00:40:08,000
When a mother is separated from her child,

579
00:40:08,000 --> 00:40:09,390
she'd of course be worried.

580
00:40:09,390 --> 00:40:12,120
When the time comes, she won't care less anymore.

581
00:40:20,730 --> 00:40:21,490
Thank you.

582
00:40:27,290 --> 00:40:28,420
This pregnant woman

583
00:40:30,040 --> 00:40:31,430
